d39d12e8065e19f01386261ab9960c62b3c3cb887d32f6207297ad60151226bf1fcd9c8f1e349a434cfe4af9bd77ceb6b138cdfabe23cfac7204647268b19ecb  0001-use-qwarning-and-exit-instead-of-qfatal-for-wayland-error.patch"
